{"tid":290484,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"试着说：「啥子玩意儿」不要说：「咩撚野」","createTime":"2017-06-19T20:09:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T10:12:51.000Z","uid":71008,"like":12,"dislike":189,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"57d8c51eef7c777d553f2df4a4c336523ea0e29b","tid":290484,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T20:09:31.000Z","msg":"前天我和老乡大老早的就出门去莎莎给家里的娘们买东西去了。买完之后俺们还顺路逛了逛优衣库（Uniqlo），我挺喜欢里面的四角裤衩，就打开包装来看，怎料有个在那里工作的妞就发现了我，说些鸟语，大概是不可以打开的意思，我就说，&ldquo;规矩？那是啥子玩意儿？&rdquo;就一把推开她走路出门。我走了几步回头发现她居然就这么哭了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港的病夫肯定不像我们东北人那么爷们。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7eee5a588d64a563cb58403ebea5daea336030","tid":290484,"uid":2945,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T20:25:57.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 做文明人講普通話 )<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做乜近排咁撚多呢啲人"},{"pid":"855edff07d0963f146739effc8272706ec820460","tid":290484,"uid":101987,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T20:27:29.000Z","msg":"差評重作 應該講埋香港是中國的"},{"pid":"47716c3fc6cca405de03329ab5c6fa98ded8b995","tid":290484,"uid":71008,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T20:38:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>差評重作 應該講埋香港是中國的</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />扯不上關係"},{"pid":"c6a398d5a09c47bd16c51d434d31bad06e146eb1","tid":290484,"uid":31669,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T20:42:52.000Z","msg":"頭果個字點撚樣讀"},{"pid":"fdc4780159720ed91e0d18d1a76f706e88cb0033","tid":290484,"uid":71008,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T20:44:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭果個字點撚樣讀</blockquote><br />\n用普通話讀就是 sha 第一聲"},{"pid":"7ee61ad7d5e069921d15151e82e0c3dea20f1839","tid":290484,"uid":73547,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T20:5